llions of good-paying jobs in the process</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 400;\">, fighting for the Green New Deal in our communities, and unite with movements for change </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>in the pursuit of the liberation of all people</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; font-weight: 400;\">. </span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent: 36pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent: 36pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong style=\"\"><em>Important Links:</em></strong></span></p><ul><li><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sign up for the hub </span><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeXadRR5eKjc2mSglKo1ZmN2o0FRLxvfkTom6egOxeCQoReiQ/viewform\">here</a></strong><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\"> and we’ll get back to you as soon as we can to get you plugged in! (No experience necessary!)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"> We have an </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>informal Full Hub checkin every other Wednesday from 4:30 to 5:30! </strong></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Open to </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>anyone</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, especially first-timers, it's a great opportunity to get to know each other better and improve our work in a chill, fun environment. </span><span style=\"font-weight: bold; background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Our Next one is Jan 13th, 2021, Joi</span><strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">n </span><a href=\"https://zoom.us/j/95316660485\">here</a></strong><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>!&nbsp;</strong>( &lt; Zoom link)</span></li><li><span style=\"background-color: transparent; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"\" id=\"docs-internal-guid-22c392f4-7fff-6c60-c059-bbeb1dd9d0b7\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>Donate to us </strong></span><a href=\"https://secure.actblue.com/donate/sunrisearlingtonmassachusetts\"><span xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" style=\"font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"><strong>here</strong></span><span xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\"> </span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 11pt; background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">to help us continue to fight for our futures and create a society centered on justice, interdependence, and community care. </span></span><br></span></li></ul><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent: 36pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><em><br></em></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;text-indent: 36pt;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong style=\"\"><em>About Us:</em></strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We lobby our reps to support vital legislation and advocate for our future, campaign for climate champions, organize actions and rallies to build community, demand change, and grow our base, and put on many trainings to teach people about Sunrise art and strategy and help them find their place in the movement.</span></p><p><strong><br></strong></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>Some of the things we’ve accomplished are</strong></span></p><ul style=\"margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;padding-inline-start:48px;\"><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Successfully campaigning for climate champion Senator Ed Markey</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">6 trainings in 2020, on topics from MA politics to orientations to action art.&nbsp;</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Art build to make merch and signs, in solidarity with the Black Lives Matter movement</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Mobilization for the Act On Mass Transparency campaign in the State House</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Collaborated with orgs like For The People Boston and Extinction Rebellion on actions and fundraisers</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">We sent postcards, phonebanked, and rose to the challenge of saving our democracy, hosting a weekend of action before the election, where we heard from inspiring speakers and held a banner drop, all to demand that we “Count Every Vote”.&nbsp;</span></p></li><li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type:disc;font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;\" aria-level=\"1\"><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\" role=\"presentation\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Even through quarantine, building community and finding moments of joy with games, events, and storytelling!</span></p></li></ul><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><br></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>There is a place for anyone in Sunrise Arlington</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, although our members and leaders are youth (under 35). </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>We have a wide variety of teams and initiatives to get involved in</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; white-space: pre-wrap;\">: Art, Campaigns/Actions, Outreach, Trainings, Communications, and Coalitions/Partnerships. </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>You don’t need any experience to join</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; white-space: pre-wrap;\">, and will join a community of welcoming and dedicated youth from high school to college and beyond. </span><span style=\"background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; white-space: pre-wrap;\"><strong>Sign up </strong><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeXadRR5eKjc2mSglKo1ZmN2o0FRLxvfkTom6egOxeCQoReiQ/viewform\" style=\"\"><strong>here</strong></a><strong> and we’ll get back to you as soon as we can to get you plugged in!&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Arial;color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">Find out more about the Sunrise Movement </span><strong><a href=\"https://www.sunrisemovement.org/?ms=SunriseMovement\">here</a>.</strong></p>","email":"SunriseArlingtonHub@gmail.com","website":"http://bit.ly/SunriseArlSignup","twitter":null,"facebook":"https://www.facebook.com/Sunrise-Arlington-MA-108270007549180/","instagram":"https://instagram.com/sunrisearlington","signup":"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1S3qHj1mcwd5Z87kmvvKEfR39aTAsUNLpr7f-eBvdEQk/edit","donations":"https://secure.actblue.com/donate/sunrisearlingtonmassachusetts","websiteText":"Sign-Up Form","logo":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1,"src":"/static/0